{"tid":1288910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［戰術］加固防線建議","createTime":"2019-07-05T23:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T01:10:29.000Z","uid":67645,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"61170c2b2d8c00ddfc6c4d439613f4051fd92bae","tid":1288910,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:13:06.000Z","msg":"發夢果陣成日見到好多人將鐵馬砌完個三角就推出去<br />\n相信大家都睇到咁多次以來都好易被敵軍擊破<br />\n問題有幾點：<br />\n1. 防線重量不足<br />\n當我地都能夠輕易推得郁嘅鐵馬，敵軍裝備體能上都比我軍優勝。攻破清拆難度不大，只需放個洋蔥，趁人群暫時散去就攻出缺口。<br />\n解決方法：<br />\n現場有大量空水樽及其他雜物，點解唔好好善用，將水樽入水綁係鐵馬上面。只要有100個700ml嘅水綁係一個鐵馬上，已經增加70kg。甚至再將膠袋裝泥土磚頭，可以大大增加防線穩固程度。而且更可向高處發展，令敵方用遠攻時亦有防禦。<br />\n<br />\n2. 前線手足未能休息<br />\n上面已提及裝備體能上差距，加上敵軍輪班制齋企只會消耗我方體力。多次嘅結果都係敵軍會趁體力消耗得七七八八時乘虛而入。<br />\n解決方法：<br />\n同上面方法差唔多，增加防線防禦能力，令前線嘅手足無需長期處於緊張作戰狀態。而後排手足亦應該定時搵人輪班，令前線有充足嘅休息。<br />\n<br />\n3. 防線只係防線 毫無阻嚇性<br />\n係敵軍眼中我地嘅防線根本可以稱為無物，佢地企係度唔係因為諗緊戰略攻破防線。只係諗緊幾時進攻，因為我軍完全無反擊嘅戰略同準備。<br />\n解決方法：<br />\n對峙時應把握時間作計劃，準備反擊及防禦用具。包括投擲物，盾，反衝鋒三角鐵馬，甚至陷阱。即使好多非勇武唔敢投擲亦可參與製作，敵軍見我地準備充足亦唔敢輕舉妄動。而計劃上亦可設計定第二防線，即使被人攻破亦能馬上聚集。<br />\n<br />\n敵軍嘅攻勢只會越黎越強硬，我地亦都需要做好心理準備，加強自己嘅防禦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567f2e6859ceb7eabcb4f1a98ca4eaf30e4c900f","tid":1288910,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809d8e45aa7208c16b969b1ff5cc7faf27681b4e","tid":1288910,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a40c16b25cfe9be7cf241593978062c57a5d2a","tid":1288910,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707134870e0b67756b33be096116ac6303541c5d","tid":1288910,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b468a0e2296a8e4cd5d9e857c3c25170e853c604","tid":1288910,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ed07e18e59fd9d22646f4ae00a6de53439c6a1","tid":1288910,"uid":257737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:16:30.000Z","msg":"不斷進步緊架啦我地"},{"pid":"eebacc7cc6dc6a3da9f07f1f0b87e25408c1d293","tid":1288910,"uid":162215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:18:42.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"226c30652eb218bb23f6edb2509a93587bcd955c","tid":1288910,"uid":189109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:22:24.000Z","msg":"唔係想撥你冷水<br />\n不過，要點樣先縛得實成lit水？人地拆返你啲水樽要幾耐？"},{"pid":"e734aacd924827fd349e556b2d3d04ca05ba33e3","tid":1288910,"uid":199101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:24:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"effe5d881e1611a8e78179141daa11814939faa0","tid":1288910,"uid":36158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:25:47.000Z","msg":"winter on fire係用雪 木板加固 <br />\n關於泥又要搵鏟<br />\n香港好難搞 無論工具定原料都有難度"},{"pid":"60bb7e8cfa3473c4f1d4c363bfe33555c9b2a2c8","tid":1288910,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T23:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnLGP4M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnLGP4M.jpg&h=99c2f6f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣係樽口打個死結 再綁上鐵馬<br />\n再唔係就用索帶"},{"pid":"10ea3ba024b5f5da3a